OL,3,CDriver who hit mum and daughter after
OL,4,Cfalling asleep given suspended sentence
OL,6,FA woman who collided with a mum and
OL,7,Fdaughter after falling asleep at the
OL,8,Fwheel of her car has avoided an
OL,9,Fimmediate prison sentence.
OL,11,FDeborah Starr, 68, was driving her
OL,12,FPeugeot 208 on Sleaford Road,
OL,13,FTattershall, Lincolnshire, when she
OL,14,Flost control on 15 August last year.
OL,16,FShe mounted the pavement and hit a 39-
OL,17,Fyear-old woman and her 11-year-old
OL,18,Fdaughter, who were "launched into the
OL,19,Fair by the force of the collision and
OL,20,Flanded near a wall in a nearby
OL,21,Fgarden", Lincolnshire Police said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
