FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781024765
OL,3,CDriver who hit mum and daughter after
OL,4,Cfalling asleep given suspended sentence
OL,6,FStarr's vehicle stopped after hitting
OL,7,Fa lamppost and witnesses called
OL,8,Femergency services.
OL,10,FThe victims had surgery to injuries
OL,11,Fincluding multiple fractures.
OL,13,FStarr, of Chipping Cross, Clevedon,
OL,14,FSomerset, admitted two offences of
OL,15,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving.
OL,18,FShe was given a two-and-a-half year
OL,19,Fprison sentence, suspended for three
OL,20,Fyears, and will have to carry out 150
OL,21,Fhours of unpaid work.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
