FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781024765
OL,3,CDriver who hit mum and daughter after
OL,4,Cfalling asleep given suspended sentence
OL,6,FShe was also banned from driving for
OL,7,Ftwo years.
OL,9,FDet Sgt Adam Doona, of Lincolnshire
OL,10,FPolice, said: "This collision was down
OL,11,Fto Deborah Starr driving whilst tired.
OL,13,F"At the time of the collision comments
OL,14,Fwere made by her that lead us to
OL,15,Fbelieve that she had fallen asleep at
OL,16,Fthe wheel, causing her to mount the
OL,17,Fpavement.
OL,26,@rD@OOU
